# Cayro Multi-Store ERP Frontend

Operational SPA for Cayro stores + HQ. Consumes `cayro-multi-store-backend` REST APIs.

**Read [`CLAUDE.md`](mdc:CLAUDE.md) first.**

## Stack (locked)

Vite · React 19 · TS · TanStack Router · TanStack Query · Zustand · shadcn/ui · Tailwind 4 · Axios · next-themes.

## Auth

Access JWT in memory (`@/lib/access-token`). Refresh in `sessionStorage`. Menu from `GET /auth/me/menu`.

## Rules

- Path alias `@/` only — never `../../../`.
- Sidebar from API — no static role→menu mapping.
- ERP UI: dense tables, badges, monospace for codes, light+dark.
- Idempotency header for store create / pickup create when implementing mutations.
